            <h3>Pokemon GO! PVP Optimization</h3>
            <h4>Co-Advisor: Dr. Jon Brown (Bakersfield College)<br>
                Students: Kevin, Pablo (BC), Ed (BC)<br>Majors: Computer Science</h4>
            <p>This project was brought to us by Dr. Brown from Bakersfield College who I met through the <a
